# opendnp3 is vendored locally per build host via `make opendnp3-vendor[-arm|-windows]`
# (fetches source, builds static libs + headers into third_party/opendnp3/).
# It's large and fully reproducible from scripts/build-opendnp3.sh, so it is not
# committed — each build host regenerates it.
/build/opendnp3/
third_party/opendnp3/

# Scratch object files from `make verify-shim`.
*.o
